2️⃣ Install Backend Dependencies

cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
3️⃣ Install Frontend Dependencies

cd frontend
npm install
4️⃣ Start Backend

uvicorn app.main:app --reload
5️⃣ Start Frontend

cd frontend
npm run dev
6️⃣ Run using Docker

docker-compose up --build -d
📜 API Endpoints
POST /logs/ → Submit log entry

GET /logs/ → Fetch logs

GET /alerts/ → Fetch alerts

GET /ai/anomaly → Run AI detection

